lps revenue grow with the shelter''s capacity."},{"type":"comparison_table","background":"","alignment":"center","heading":"The Animal Pride Advantage","left_label":"Traditional Fundraising","right_label":"Animal Pride","rows":[{"left":"Campaign-based — requires active staff effort to launch","right":"Always on — revenue flows year-round without campaigns"},{"left":"Donor fatigue risk from repeated donation appeals","right":"Joy-based purchasing — products people genuinely want"},{"left":"Staff-heavy — design, inventory, and fulfillment burden","right":"Fully managed — printing, fulfillment, and support included"},{"left":"Short-term impact from one-off drives","right":"Recurring revenue with growing adopter loyalty"}],"note":""},{"type":"form_cta","background":"#00698f","alignment":"center","heading":"Let Your Adoptions Keep Giving","body":"Animal Pride helps humane societies turn love, pride, and storytelling into lasting impact — without adding work, cost, or complexity.","button_label":"Schedule a Partnership Demo","button_link":"/apply"}]}' WHERE `slug` = 'pricing-revenue-share';
